This project contains a very simple math calculator base the specs you can find in ./docs

To can use this calculator on a console.

npm install
npm start


Sample Session Run after npm start:

===== Very Basic Calculator - Command Line ====
----- Enter a question following the examples below
----- What is 5? =>  5
----- What    is    5? =>  5
----- What 5? =>  error
----- type exit to exit 
ENTER MATH QUESTION: What is 4?
4
ENTER MATH QUESTION: 


use npm test to run all unit tests